title: Dante_Intro
---
<<party_join Dante>>
When I had journeyed half of our life's way, #card:Dante
I found myself within a shadowed forest,
for I had lost the path that does not stray. #task:Hilltop
<<target Hilltop>>
<<SetActive false area_init>>
<<SetActive true area_hilltop>>
